WebService-EBC

Version 0.01
2011-December

Simple spider to fetch news and media from EBC 
(Empresa Brasileira de Comunicacao)

The EBC website serve a rss feed that is the main basis for this module.
The spider finds some id tags and classes from the html codes in EBC to
parse the news and media.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc WebService::EBC

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=WebService-EBC

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/WebService-EBC

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/WebService-EBC

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/WebService-EBC/


